text: Oricopis maculiventris is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Lea in 1917. It is known from Australia.BioLib.cz - Oricopis maculiventris. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1917
